This is the PEIS-kernel middleware for the Ecologies of Physically
Embedded Intelligent Systems project. For a description of this
project and it's goals see http://www.aass.oru.se/~peis

To install this middleware and a few sample applications to test it
read the file INSTALL. 

Remember that you also probably want to download and install a couple
of real PEIS components that can achive some functionalties. If you
want to write your own components please take a look under the samples
directory to find examples of how to use the API functions.

